      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="35842dd3-aa3e-4b2b-9718-c74d09d2713d" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Lương, tiền công (thường trả theo giờ, ngày, hoặc tuần)</Vi>
          <En>Money paid by an employer to an employee, typically calculated on an hourly, daily, or weekly basis.</En>
          <Example>She receives her wages every Friday in cash.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="ff00d688-2388-4377-8ef7-9aca2c412ce1">
              <Vi>Một công nhân nhận tiền lương hàng tuần từ chủ lao động.</Vi>
              <En>A worker receives weekly pay from their employer.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="312107ac-c70c-48d1-931c-e01bdfbb3f44">
              <Vi>Chính phủ đề xuất tăng mức lương tối thiểu.</Vi>
              <En>The government proposed raising the minimum wage.</En>
